data.description: Don't miss this beautiful 10-acre parcel that features a 3-bedroom 2-bathroom 2240 square foot home on a walk-out basement with a concrete patio. The property features a large wooded area great for hunting and recreational fun.  The HUGE wrap-around deck is perfect for entertaining and relaxing on summer evenings overlooking the front pasture, fire pit area and woods.  There is a 30x40 pole barn that has electric installed and would be great for 4H or horses. There is an abundance of wildlife here with many deer and turkeys running around. The new metal roof is only 7 years old. All new kitchen appliances installed in 2022. This home has it all and the land to go with it.
